main install

Install a package

USAGE:
    main install [OPTIONS] <PACKAGE>

ARGUMENTS:
        <PACKAGE>
            Package name to install

OPTIONS:
    -g, --[no-]global
            Install globally
    -f, --[no-]force
            Force reinstall even if already installed
